{
    "author_name": "Datadog",
    "description": "## Windows Certificate Store Integration Dashboard\n\nThis is an example Windows Certificate Store dashboard demonstrating the information that the integration collects.\n\nFor further reading, see:\n\n- [Windows Certificate Store Integration Documentation](https://docs.datadoghq.com/integrations/windows-certificate/)",
